      "announcement_url": null,
      "experiment_goals": "Feedback from partners determining:\n- Effects on user sign-in times for the trial group\n- Effects on user sign-in success rates for the trial group\n- Relative performance of showing Chrome UI before system UI for single platform passkey availability, vs not showing it\n\nChrome development team to assess:\n- User rates of acceptance vs dismissal of sign-in UI\n- Distribution of number of credentials being displayed, and the usage of default-selected vs other credentials\n- Latency of UI being shown, or promise rejection",
